									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/economics/workers/telework-telecommuting-inequality-research-coronavirus/" rel="bookmark" title="The inequality of telework: 5 studies you should know about">
										<span class="rthumb">
